title: VS Code Copilot Resource Sync
message: "If you use or reference vscode-copilot-sync, please cite it as below."
type: software
version: 2.2.0
date-released: "2026-05-21"
authors:
  - family-names: Tout
    given-names: Chris
    alias: CTOUT
repository-code: https://github.com/CTOUT/vscode-copilot-sync
url: https://github.com/CTOUT/vscode-copilot-sync
abstract: >
  A PowerShell toolkit to sync, install, and manage GitHub Copilot agents,
  instructions, hooks, skills, workflows, and plugins from the awesome-copilot
  community catalogue into VS Code. Full lifecycle management — install, update,
  and remove — tracked via subscription manifests. Works on Windows, macOS, and
  Linux via PowerShell 7+.
keywords:
  - github-copilot
  - vscode
  - powershell
  - developer-tools
  - automation
  - awesome-copilot
  - plugins
